title: Diving in a Kelp Forest (Premium)
description:
This is a preview episode. Get the full episode, and many more, ad free, on our supporter's feed: https://getsleepy.com/support.


Diving in a Kelp Forest
Tonight, we’ll dive off the coast of Southern California, where an underwater forest of giant kelp forms a vertical sanctuary for hundreds of dazzling sea creatures. 😴 

Sound design: sailing on the ocean. ⛵️🌊
Narrator: Thomas Jones
